<section id="sounds" class="doc-section">
  <h1 class="page-title">Sounds</h1>
  <p><a href="#home">&#8592; Home</a></p>
  <hr />
  <p>All audio files live in the <code>assets/sounds/</code> directory, organized into categorized subdirectories. All sound files use the <code>.wav</code> format. SDL2_mixer handles both short sound effects (<code>Mix_Chunk</code> via <code>Mix_LoadWAV</code>) and streaming music (<code>Mix_Music</code> via <code>Mix_LoadMUS</code>).</p>
